name: Sidon architectural model
description:
This model is discodiffusion inspired fantasy architecture. It has been trained only on buildings, clouds, water etc and not people. This is a fun model to use when making cities or building scenes. Trained from 1.5.


Token is Sidon or Sidon style. In a prompt... Sidon, city of the future.

meta.prompt: sidon style, City of progress, futuristic city, utopian world, shiny great colors,prosperous buildings, high class clothes and architectural designs, luxurious constructions, utopian futur, highly detailed, hdr, perfect, stunning progressive architecture, flawless world, reflective surfaces, subsurface scattering, flawless buildings, beyond imagination, 8K, global illumination, wide angle, god rays, dream world
